70-BLK-2G32TT-NoBashGuard-c-Side.png?resize=2000,2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118640001-AM-FCXX-EAGLE-Q174CL55-DUB170-BLK-2G32TT-NoBashGuard-c-Side.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118640001-AM-FCXX-EAGLE-Q174CL55-DUB170-BLK-2G32TT-NoBashGuard-c-Side.png?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118640001-AM-FCXX-EAGLE-Q174CL55-DUB170-BLK-2G32TT-NoBashGuard-c-Side.png?resize=1800,1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118640001-AM-FCXX-EAGLE-Q174CL55-DUB170-BLK-2G32TT-NoBashGuard-c-Side.png?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118640001-AM-FCXX-EAGLE-Q174CL55-DUB170-BLK-2G32TT-NoBashGuard-c-Side.png?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118640001-AM-FCXX-EAGLE-Q174CL55-DUB170-BLK-2G32TT-NoBashGuard-c-Side.png?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118640001-AM-FCXX-EAGLE-Q174CL55-DUB170-BLK-2G32TT-NoBashGuard-c-Side.png?resize=2048,2048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3000\" height=\"3000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?resize=2000,2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?resize=1800,1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/006118637001-AM-FCXXSL-EGL-SPRPMQ168CL55DUB170BLK34TT-c-Side-v02.png?resize=2048,2048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3>Cranksets</h3>\n<p>In a departure from SRAM’s 3-bolt direct-mount crank and chainring system, the new Transmission cranksets feature an 8-bolt interface aligned with “T-Type” compatibility throughout the system. SRAM touts the hollow core carbon fiber XX SL to still be the lightest on the market and the XX crankset features foam core carbon arms with a removable bash guard. SRAM refer to the XO crankset, with a balanced stiffness-to-weight ratio, as “the most advanced aluminum crankset we’ve ever made”; it, too, includes a removable bash guard. New 8-bolt direct mount chainrings are available in four sizes from 32-38T and two offset variants (0 and +3).</p>\n<h3>Cassettes and Chains</h3>\n<p><em>The harder you pedal, the better it shifts.</em> SRAM boasts that Transmission’s design enables riders to shift more efficiently (seamlessly, even) under high pedaling load. A major part of this enhanced rideability comes from T-Type cassette/derailleur interface. Without interference from a traditional derailleur hanger, Transmission cassettes and derailleurs make direct contact with each other “ensuring perfect alignment on every bike.” The new cassettes retain a 520% gear range but have an improved progression ramp with 44 and 38T cogs in the low end as compared to the 42-36T steps in 10-52T Eagle cassettes.</p>\n<p>The Transmission cassette sits 2.5mm closer to the dropout than a traditional Eagle cassette in order to work better with the growing number of frames built with wider 55mm chainlines. These nudge the chainring 3mm further outboard than the 52mm chainline normally paired with Boost 148mm hub spacing. That’s just one of a few reasons why Transmission and non-Transmission components can not be mixed and matched. Also, SRAM totally remapped the shift ramps and tooth profiles on the Transmission cassette, aiding both in durability and shifting precision.</p>\n<p>T-type cassettes all have a dedicated setup cog for chain placement when configuring the system. As is often the case, material spec and distribution dictate pricing and advertised durability with the lightest weight being the spendiest. Flattop T-Type chains are designed to optimize Transmission performance, offering “shift when you want performance” and are the strongest chains SRAM have ever made.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/Transmission-4.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/Transmission-4.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/Transmission-4.jpg?resize=1024,682&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/Transmission-4.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/Transmission-4.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/Transmission-4.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/Transmission-4.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/Transmission-4.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3000\" height=\"3000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=2000,2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=1800,1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018308001-EC-AXS-POD-ULTIMATE-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=2048,2048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3000\" height=\"3000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?w=3000&amp;quality=75 3000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=2000,2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=1800,1800&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=1335,1335&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=1536,1536&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/03/003018312001-EC-AXS-POD-RGHT-BRIDGE-WMMX-c-3q.png?resize=2048,2048&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3>AXS Shift Pod Controllers</h3>\n<p>The new AXS Shift Pods are the only component released with Transmission that is backward compatible with Eagle AXS groups. That also means that, if you like the previous styles of AXS shifters, they’ll work fine with a Transmission derailleur. Feature highlights include a two-button “click and fire” design, button command personalization, interchangeable right/left mounting, and lots of adjustability. The deluxe version includes replaceable concave/convex buttons. They are also lighter weight than the previous generation controls.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.co